SurvOT-Rank- (45_otehv2_rankevent) — Optimal-transport-induced event hazard
decomposition for multimodal cancer survival analysis, with pairwise ranking
supervision and gated event aggregation.

Copyright (c) 2026 LDT-von

This work reuses the data-loading pipeline, slot attention, omics encoder and
survival loss functions from:

    SlotSPE: Slot-based Survival with Positional Encoding
    (Zhang et al., ICLR 2026)
    https://github.com/zylvemvet/SlotSPE

